{"tid":826414,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無ching試過達文西睡眠法？","createTime":"2018-09-18T08:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T15:04:24.000Z","uid":5190,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e99c154c4a9530dd770c447d26b3a610a6c8bc0a","tid":826414,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:30:12.000Z","msg":"多階段睡眠的支持者認為，這種方法可以令時間過得更為充實，可以在一星期內節約20-30個小時，並且精力更加充沛。相傳達&middot;文西就是採用多相性睡眠，他每隔4個小時就睡15分鐘。<br />\n多階段睡眠在開始實行時的一至兩周內是很難接受的，測試結果表明受測者並沒有受到這種將睡眠分散成若干個小睡眠片段方式的影響<br />\n<br />\n美國加州大學的睡眠專家莎拉・梅德尼克等人認為，多相睡眠會破壞人體的晝夜節律，導致身心疲倦、焦慮緊張、免疫力下降等不良反應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無清試過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n硬係覺得其中一次會瞓瞓下死咗"},{"pid":"002ea25fda7ce1b9afa7e44d517af21a9c0c3870","tid":826414,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:31:06.000Z","msg":"你有冇試過？"},{"pid":"e36e814cfcdc17118ddfa9c34a97f5f216816c4f","tid":826414,"uid":136186,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"所以達文西死撚咗啦"},{"pid":"eef82bbcff08662e33228bb1b5658898eebdb5ec","tid":826414,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"002ea25fda7ce1b9afa7e44d517af21a9c0c3870","tid":826414,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:31:06.000Z","msg":"你有冇試過？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:35:26.000Z","msg":"無 我係啲一日唔瞓12粒鐘唔會醒嘅人 所以無可能試到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a0bfd4ce56b50c7c2be20d978d182f74dde783","tid":826414,"uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e36e814cfcdc17118ddfa9c34a97f5f216816c4f","tid":826414,"uid":136186,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"所以達文西死撚咗啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T08:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse