"msg":"港奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18072e896f91507980413b0e72fcc98e49e255e0","tid":826414,"uid":63843,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:01:39.000Z","msg":"我睇過果隻係分割式睡眠 <br />\n一日訓四次 每次兩個鐘 <br />\n訓4次夠八個鐘=正常人睡眠時間<br />\n<br />\n原理係每次訓醒大腦都有幾粒鐘黃金時間<br />\n訓4次醒4次 = 有4次黃金時間<br />\n比起一次訓8個鐘得一段黃金時間 做野會更有效率<br />\n<br />\n利申未試過"},{"pid":"3bf82fdd601c35ffa1eeae7b2d4734dd2d809827","tid":826414,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:50:15.000Z","msg":"聞西睡眠法?<br />\n攞你命3000"},{"pid":"c3c2c6cd28d432a336f5409182ce0c30deb3c258","tid":826414,"uid":73,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:57:19.000Z","msg":"我試過每日訓十個鐘, 然後每4個鐘再訓個半鐘"},{"pid":"68f86a06681cac34f4b804856b5c26cc70af3e14","tid":826414,"uid":27935,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T06:15:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"827f240fe72666e862a6bee3e76980e5a7add84e","tid":826414,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66805a1b50ca6487cc8d157d02bc80d2839cd2bc","tid":826414,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T08:30:33.000Z","msg":"人地咪同左你講有咩壞囉，想早死啲嘅咪試下囉"},{"pid":"a596ed11467f790ce4af29dcf066c15256011f2a","tid":826414,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:05:24.000Z","msg":"以前試過為左考試咁樣溫書法，<br />\n代價係而家集中力、記憶力係殘廢級數，<br />\n睡眠質素都變到極差。"},{"pid":"1bf2b0d0f39da8a29cebc6bb42dcddd6fe3e0388","tid":826414,"uid":92500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}